metadata.name: Scorpio Witch #1
metadata.description:
< CLOTHES: Summer Dorm Uniform >
 Summer dorm students tend to be active, diplomatic, and optimistic.
 They are good at making friends and acting in groups.

< WAND: Tranquility Wand >
 A staff handed down from generation to generation in the closed land of snow.
 It contains the magic power of ice.
 It creates a world of frozen silence. It also makes the user more patient.

< MAGIC: Heat Of Desert Wind >
 A dry, searing wind is generated, scorching the hostile's skin and cutting it with the fast wind.
